%2FoRylDOxwbH%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Dr%20Avdhesh%20Yadav%20(%40Avdheshyadavsp)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAvdheshyadavsp%2Fstatus%2F1800148082455425252%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJune%2010%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20student%20secured%20an%20all-India%20rank%20of%201%2C321%20in%20the%20National%20Eligibility%20cum%20Entrance%20Test%20(NEET)-UG%2C%20having%20scored%20705%20out%20of%20720%20in%20NEET.%20Her%20NEET%20score%20put%20her%20in%20the%20top%2099.94%20percentile%2C%20which%20typically%20gets%20a%20student%20a%20seat%20in%20one%20of%20the%20top%20medical%20colleges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20aspiring%20doctors%20are%20required%20to%20clear%20this%20exam%20to%20get%20into%20medical%20courses%20across%20the%20country%2C%20though%20board%20marks%20also%20hold%20weight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20March%20board%20exam%2C%20she%20managed%20only%2031%20(out%20of%20100)%20marks%20in%20chemistry%20(theory)%20and%2021%20in%20physics%20(theory)%20in%20the%20Gujarat%20Secondary%20and%20Higher%20Secondary%20Board%20(GSEB)%20exam.%20She%20barely%20passed%20in%20biology%20(theory)%20with%2039%20marks%2C%20her%20marksheet%20showed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20supplementary%20exams%2C%20she%20scored%2022%20in%20physics%20and%20got%20just%20the%20passing%20marks%20of%2033%20in%20chemistry.%20Her%20boards%20and%20NEET%20marksheets%20went%20viral%20after%20the%20centre-wise%20and%20city-wise%20NEET-UG%20results%20were%20declared%20-%20both%20having%20the%20same%20first%2C%20middle%2C%20and%20last%20names.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20NEET%20results%20will%20not%20help%20her%20get%20a%20seat%20in%20any%20medical%20college%20in%20the%20country%20due%20to%20her%20poor%20marks%20in%20board%20exams.%20Her%20NEET%20score%20has%20also%20come%20under%20scrutiny%20amid%20allegations%20of%20paper%20leak%20and%20grace%20marks%20awarded%20to%20some%20students%20in%20the%20NEET%20exam%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20complaint%2C%20a%20total%20of%201%2C500%20students%20were%20given%20grace%20marks.%20The%20National%20Testing%20Agency%20(NTA)%2C%20tasked%20with%20conducting%20the%20nationwide%20exam%2C%20had%20formed%20a%20grievance%20redressal%20panel%20which%20had%20awarded%20grace%20marks%20to%20the%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20later%20scrapped%20the%20grace%20marks%2C%20which%20reduced%20the%20student's%20NEET%20score%20to%20700.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20inputs%20from%20Mahendra%20Prasad%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722585660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F8kin8q6g_entrance-exam-generic_625x300_14_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fstudent-aces-neet-fails-in-class-12-chemistry-physics-marksheet-viral-6246084%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20student%20in%20Gujarat%20who%20allegedly%20failed%20her%20board%20exams%20in%20March%20has%20hit%20the%20headlines%20for%20her%20stellar%20performance%20in%20the%20NEET-UG%20medical%20entrance%20exam.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fstudent-aces-neet-fails-in-class-12-chemistry-physics-marksheet-viral-6246084%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fstudent-aces-neet-fails-in-class-12-chemistry-physics-marksheet-viral-6246084%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fstudent-aces-neet-fails-in-class-12-chemistry-physics-marksheet-viral-6246084%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Air%20India%20Suspends%20Tel%20Aviv%20Flights%20Amid%20Escalating%20Middle%20East%20Tensions%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAir%20India%20today%20suspended%20its%20flights%20to%20and%20from%20Israel's%20Tel%20Aviv%20with%20immediate%20effect%20till%20August%208%20amid%20escalating%20tensions%20in%20the%20Middle%20E