ars%2C%20after%20Russia's%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%20triggered%20sweeping%20sanctions%20to%20lock%20Moscow%20out%20of%20the%20US%20dollar-based%20global%20financial%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20week%2C%20Swiss%20bank%20UBS%20joined%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fde-dollarization-dollar-war-usd-yuan-china-russia-brics-currency-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eanalysts%20pushing%20back%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20de-dollarization%20narrative%2C%20saying%20a%20US%20dollar-centric%20world%20will%20persist%20%26quot%3Bfor%20years%20to%20come.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20several%20currencies%20and%20commodities%20%E2%80%94%20particularly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdedollarization-china-allied-central-banks-hoard-gold-dollar-weaponization-record-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egold%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20will%20play%20%26quot%3Bcritical%20roles%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20shifting%20world%20currency%20regime%2C%20Alejo%20Czerwonko%2C%20UBS'%20CIO%20of%20emerging%20markets%20in%20the%20Americas%2C%20wrote%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ubs.com%2Fglobal%2Fen%2Fwealth-management%2Fwho-we-serve%2Fmarketnews%2Farticle.1621092.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMonday%20note.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20dollar's%20strong%20dominance%20is%20mainly%20because%20it's%20very%20entrenched%20in%20the%20global%20financial%20system%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bis.org%2Fstatistics%2Frpfx22_fx.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eextremely%20liquid.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20also%20offers%20deep%20derivatives%20markets%20%E2%80%94%20forwards%2C%20swaps%2C%20options%2C%20etc.%20%E2%80%94%20giving%20market%20participants%20the%20ability%20to%20hedge%20exposure%20efficiently%2C%26quot%3B%20UBS'%20Czerwonko%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20no%20close%20competing%20currencies%20to%20the%20dollar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20greenback%20is%20used%20in%20about%2050%25%20of%20all%20global%20payments%20and%2084%25%20of%20trade%20finance%20contracts%20%E2%80%94%20far%20outpacing%20its%20closest%20competitor%2C%20the%20euro%2C%20which%20accounts%20for%2023%25%20of%20all%20global%20payments%20and%20just%206%25%20of%20trade%20finance%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.swift.com%2Four-solutions%2Fcompliance-and-shared-services%2Fbusiness-intelligence%2Frenminbi%2Frmb-tracker%2Frmb-tracker-document-centre%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESWIFT%20data.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20currency%20still%20accounts%20for%20the%20lion's%20share%20of%20global%20foreign%20exchange%20reserves%20%E2%80%94%2060%25%20of%20the%20FX%20holdings%20of%20central%20banks%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.imf.org%2Fen%2FBlogs%2FArticles%2F2024%2F06%2F11%2Fdollar-dominance-in-the-international-reserve-system-an-update%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInternational%20Monetary%20Fund%20data.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20comparison%2C%20the%20Chinese%20yuan%20accounts%20for%20less%20than%205%25%20of%20global%20payments%20and%20trade%20finance%2C%20separately.%20It%20also%20accounts%20for%20just%202.3%25%20of%20global%20reserves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20currency%20competitors%20are%20lagging%20behind%20the%20greenback%2C%20this%20doesn't%20mean%20the%20dollar%20has%20no%20other%20competitors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUBS%20and%20a%20separate%20Bloomberg%20Intelligence%20report%20released%20on%20Wednesday%20flagged%20gold%20as%20a%20standout%20among%20competitors%20chipping%20away%20at%20the%20dollar.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fcommodities%2Fgold-price%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espot%20gold%20price%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20now%20trading%20at%20record%20highs%20around%20%242%2C500%20an%20ounce%20thanks%20to%20strong%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20amount%20of%20gold%20holdings%20in%20global%20reserves%20has%20doubled%20in%20just%20over%20five%20years%2C%20according%20to%20Bloomberg%20Intelligence%20analysis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20the%20yellow%20metal%20carries%20no%20credit%20or%20counter-party%20risk%2C%20some%20deem%20it%20as%20being%20better%20insulated%20from%20financial%20sanctions%2C%20particularly%20those%20from%20the%20emerging%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20UBS'%20Czerwonko.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22de1dbf77-2ca8-4c60-b8d2-23a39cf4dd5e%5C%22%3EUS%20political%20concerns%20influence%20the%20dollar%2C%20but%20there%20are%20issues%20for%20competing%20currencies%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20the%20dollar%20is%20unlikely%20to%20be%20dethroned%20anytime%20soon%2C%20there%20are%20fears%20about%20political%20risks%20in%20the%20US%20as%20election%20season%20begins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20%26quot%3BUS%20political%20atmosphere%26quot%3B%20and%20large%20fiscal%20deficit%20are%20experiencing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fdedollarization-dollar-dominance-us-politics-economy-trade-fed-china-yuan-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eserious%20issues%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20investors%20are%20concerned%20about%2C%20UBS'%20Czerwonko%20thinks%20they%20aren't%20enough%20to%20topple%20the%20dollar%20from%20its%20perch%20as%20the%20world's%20reserve%20currency%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20situation%20in%20competing%20jurisdictions%20is%20also%20dire%3B%20in%20the%20land%20of%20the%20blind%2C%20the%20one-eyed%20man%20can%20remain%20king%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Czerwonko.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20all%2C%20the%20US%20still%20ranks%20highly%20for%20market%20openness%2C%20regulatory%20quality%20and%20efficiency%2C%20and%20the%20rule%20of%20law.%20The%20AI%20technology%20revolution%20is%20also%20centered%20in%20the%20US%2C%20%26quot%3Bcementing%20the%20country's%20reputation%20for%20innovation%20and%20acting%20like%20a%20magnet%20for%20foreign%20capital%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENonetheless%2C%20foreign%20investors%20are%20watching%20the%20US%20electoral%20race%20%26quot%3Bwith%20angst%2C%26quot%3B%20Czerwonko%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20issued%20this%20warning%3A%20%26quot%3BAlthough%20shifts%20in%20the%20global%20currency%20order%20typically%20take%20place%20at%20a%20glacial%20pace%2C%20rising%20geopolitical%20tensions%20can%20trigger%20quicker%20adjustments.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20Bloomberg%20Intelligence%20said%20said%20a%20Wednesday%20report%20that%20a%20potential%20second%20Trump%20term%20could%20hasten%20a%20global%20currency%20regime%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAny%20title%20toward%20isolationism%20in%20a%20Trump%20second%20term%2C%20such%20as%20altered%20US%20attitudes%20toward%20its%20role%20in%20NATO%20and%20international%20affairs%20would%20spur%20de-dollarization%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Bloomberg%20Intelligence%20analysts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Chinese%20yuan%20is%20already%20the%20%26quot%3Bconfirmed%20rival%20to%20the%20dollar%20in%20emerging%20markets%2C%26quot%3B%20per%20Bloomberg%20Intelligence.%20Other%20rivals%20include%20the%20Indian%20rupee%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fdedollarization-dollar-dominance-us-politics-economy-trade-fed-china-yuan-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ealternative%20initiatives%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20groupings%20like%20BRICS.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAny%20major%20changes%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20slow%20and%20far%20into%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGlobal%20currency%20regimes%20are%20sticky%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Czerwonko.%20%26quot%3BEven%20as%20great%20economic%20powers%20rise%20and%20fall%2C%20their%20currencies'%20reserve%20status%20tends%20to%20survive%20well%20past%20the%20peak%20of%20their%20influence.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdedollarization-outlook-us-dol