0spaceship%2C%20they%20have%20been%20stuck%20there%20for%2057%20days%20and%20counting%2C%20with%20their%20return%20delayed%20indefinitely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sec.gov%2Fix%3Fdoc%3D%2FArchives%2Fedgar%2Fdata%2F0000012927%2F000001292724000055%2Fba-20240630.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWednesday%20SEC%20filing%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Boeing%20said%20that%20because%20of%20the%20delays%2C%20it%20has%20%26quot%3Bincreased%20the%20reach-forward%20loss%20on%20the%20program%20by%20%24125%20(million).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20on%20top%20of%20the%20%24288%20million%20additional%20loss%20that%20the%20company%20had%20projected%20in%202023%2C%20per%20the%20filing.%20This%20was%20when%20it%20first%20delayed%20the%20Starliner's%20launch%20after%20identifying%20problems%20with%20the%20aircraft's%20tests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20get%20go%2C%20the%20Starliner%20launch%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboeing-starliner-takes-off-crewed-astronauts-onboard-delays-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplagued%20by%20delays%3C%2Fa%3E%20due%20to%20technical%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20May%206%2C%20a%20pressure%20relief%20valve%20in%20the%20Atlas%205%20rocket%20led%20to%20the%20first%20delay.%20Then%2C%20on%20June%201%2C%20there%20was%20an%20issue%20with%20the%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbsnews.com%2Fnews%2Fboeing-starliner-launch-first-piloted-test-flight-halted-again-international-space-station%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20ground%20computers%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20orchestrated%20the%20final%20countdown%2C%20which%20led%20to%20a%20second%20delay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20eventual%20launch%20on%20June%205%20was%20successful%2C%20one%20of%20Starliner's%2028%20Reaction%20Control%20System%20(RCS)%20thrusters%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnasa-astronauts-speak-out-boeing-starliner-spaceship-issues-space-station-2024-7%5C%22