ps%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66ac6f56393cd3c8629acf1f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223648%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20federal%20judge%20tossed%20a%20verdict%20against%20the%20NFL%20awarding%20%244.7%20billion%20in%20damages%2C%20but%20plaintiffs%20are%20likely%20to%20appeal.%3Cp%3EIcon%20Sportswire%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20federal%20judge%20overturned%20a%20%244.7%20billion%20verdict%20in%20a%20big%20lawsuit%20against%20the%20NFL.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20judge%20dismissed%20two%20key%20witnesses'%20testimonies%20after%20deeming%20their%20methodologies%20flawed.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20plaintiffs%20are%20likely%20to%20appeal%20the%20case.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20NFL%20landed%20a%20significant%2C%20albeit%20likely%20temporary%2C%20legal%20victory%20as%20a%20federal%20judge%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.courtlistener.com%2Frecap%2Fgov.uscourts.cacd.635536%2Fgov.uscourts.cacd.635536.1513.0_1.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoverturned%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20%244.7%20billion%20verdict%20against%20the%20league.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20US%20District%20Judge%20Philip%20S.%20Gutierrez%20tossed%20a%20jury's%20judgment%20over%20the%20NFL's%20Sunday%20games%20distribution.%20Gutierrez%20wrote%20that%20the%20evidence%20did%20not%20support%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnfl-sunday-ticket-subscribers-can-get-piece-of-billions-damages-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%244.7%20billion%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20damages%20awarded%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202015%2C%20subscribers%20of%20the%20league's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-watch-super-bowl-most-nfl-games-sunday-ticket-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BSunday%20Ticket%26quot%3B%20package%3C%2Fa%3E%20sued%20the%20league%20for%20violating%20antitrust%20laws%20by%20colluding%20with%20DirecTV%2C%20a%20television%20service%20provider%2C%20to%20charge%20higher%20prices.%20The%20jury%20initially%20awarded%20%244.7%20billion%20in%20damages%2C%20which%20could%20have%20been%20tripled%20to%20%2414%20billion%20under%20federal%20antitrust%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGutierrez%20criticized%20the%20jury's%20method%20for%20calculating%20the%20damages%2C%20which%20compared%20the%20list%20price%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BSunday%20Ticket%26quot%3B%20in%202018%20and%202019%20to%20the%20average%20price%20paid%20by%20subscribers%20over%20several%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20found%20this%20approach%20flawed%20because%20it%20only%20reflects%20the%20difference%20in%20the%20amount%20paid%20from%20the%20listed%20price%20rather%20than%20estimating%20the%20damages%20from%20the%20NFL's%20supposed%20monopolistic%20behavior.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20wrote%20that%20two%20key%20witnesses'%20testimony%20should%20be%20excluded.%20Daniel%20Rascher%20and%20John%20Zona's%20testimonies%20were%20supposed%20to%20show%20that%20subscribers%20would%20have%20paid%20less%20if%20the%20NFL%20hadn't%20made%20a%20deal%20with%20DirecTV%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.courtlistener.com%2Frecap%2Fgov.uscourts.cacd.635536%2Fgov.uscourts.cacd.635536.1513.0_1.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20judge%20wrote%3C%2Fa%3E.%20However%2C%20he%20deemed%20their%20models%20unreliable%20and%20%26quot%3Bnot%20products%20of%20sound%20methodologies%2C%26quot%3B%20ultimately%20dismissing%20them%20from%20consideration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWithout%20the%20testimonials%20from%20both%20witnesses%2C%20Gutierrez%20found%20the%20jury's%20methodologies%20flawed%20and%20wrote%20that%20damages%20were%20awarded%20%26quot%3Bbased%20on%20improperly%20considered%20evidence.%26quot%3B%20The%20jury%20had%20also%20ignored%20Gutierrez's%20instructions%20and%20performed%20their%20own%20overcharge%20calculations%2C%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20that%20the%20NFL's%20media%20distribution%20model%20provides%20our%20fans%20with%20an%20array%20of%20options%20to%20follow%20the%20game%20they%20love%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20the%20NFL%20on%20X.%20The%20league%20also%20thanked%20Gutierrez%20for%20his%20%26quot%3Btime%20and%20attention%20to%20this%20case.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELawyers%20for%20the%20plaintiffs%20didn't%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20class-action%20lawsuit%20included%20over%20two%20million%20residential%20subscribers%20and%2048%2C000%20businesses%20that%20bought%20the%20telecast%20package%20between%202011%20and%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20judge%20ruled%20in%20favor%20of%20the%20NFL%2C%20plaintiffs%20are%20likely%20to%20appeal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffederal-judge-overturns-jury-verdict-nfl-billions-damages-likely-appeal-2024-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722580936000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66ac70ed393cd3c8629acf2b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffederal-judge-overturns-jury-verdict-nfl-billions-damages-likely-appeal-2024-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20federal%20judge%20overturned%20a%20%244.7%20billion%20antitrust%20verdict%20against%20the%20NFL%20for%20its%20%26quot%3BSunday%20Ticket%26quot%3B%20packages.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lwee%40insider.com%20(Lian%20Kit%20Wee)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A22%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffederal-judge-overturns-jury-verdict-nfl-billions-damages-likely-appeal-2024-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Terminator%20Zero%3A%20Trailer%20details%2C%20release%20%26amp%3B%20more%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722580811000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-112216289%2Cimgsize-13986.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fn