dhakrishnan%20and%20including%20former%20AIIMS%20(Delhi)%20Director%20Dr%20Randeep%20Guleria%20-%20time%20till%20September%2030%20to%20present%20its%20report.%20The%20committee%20has%20been%20tasked%20with%20analysing%20the%20entire%20examination%20process%20and%20suggest%20changes%20to%20make%20it%20more%20efficient.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BReport%20of%20committee%20to%20be%20submitted%20by%20September%2030%20to%20the%20government.%20Ministry%20of%20Education%20shall%20report%20compliance%20of%20committee%20and%20decision%20to%20implement%20(measures)%20in%20two%20weeks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20offered%20eight%20points%20to%20guide%20the%20committee%2C%20including%20laying%20out%20a%20standard%20operating%20procedure%2C%20or%20protocol%2C%20for%20conduct%20of%20qualifying%20exams%2C%20a%20review%20of%20process%20of%20allotting%20exam%20centres%20and%20enhanced%20identity%20checks%20of%20candidates%2C%20and%20CCTV%20monitoring%20of%20exam%20centres.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20point%20was%20to%20ensure%20%26quot%3Bsecure%20logistics%20providers%20for%20ensuring%20non-tampering%20of%20question%20papers%26quot%3B%3B%20this%20is%20crucial%20given%20the%202024%20NEET-UG%20exam%20papers%20may%20have%20been%20leaked%20while%20they%20were%20being%20transported%20-%20in%20locked%20boxes%20-%20from%20where%20they%20were%20printed%20to%20the%20exam%20centres.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20larger%20question%20of%20leaked%20exam%20papers%2C%20the%20court%20said%20it%20was%20satisfied%20%26quot%3Bthere%20was%20no%20systemic%20breach...%20the%20leak%20was%20limited%20to%20Patna%20(in%20Bihar)%20and%20Hazaribagh%20(in%20Jharkhand)%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneet-leak-hazaribagh-paper-leak-oasis-school-cbi-neet-ug-paper-leak-had-genesis-in-hazaribagh-zeroing-in-on-school-cbi-officials-6078152%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHazaribagh%20leak%20has%20been%20flagged%20as%20'Ground%20Zero'%20by%20the%20CBI%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20has%20been%20tasked%20with%20investigating%20a%20nation-wide%20'solver%20gang'%20racket%20that%20leaks%20question%20papers.%20The%20agency%20has%20made%20multiple%20arrests%20since%2C%20including%20a%20man%20called%20Rakesh%20Ranjan%2C%20alias%20Rocky%2C%20the%20alleged%20kingpin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneet-ug-paper-leak-case-cbi-arrests-rajesh-ranjan-alias-rocky-cbi-arrests-rocky-alleged-mastermind-in-neet-ug-paper-leak-case-6083484%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECBI%20Arrests%20'Rocky'%2C%20Alleged%20Mastermind%20In%20NEET%20Paper%20Leak%20Case%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20central%20agency%20has%20also%20filed%20its%20first%20chargesheet%20in%20this%20case.%20It%20has%20named%2013%20people%2C%20including%20four%20candidates%2C%20a%20junior%20engineer%20and%20two%20individuals%20labelled%20as%20'kingpins'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcandidates-parents-kingpins-named-in-cbis-1st-neet-chargesheet-6242838%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECandidates%2C%20Parents%2C%20'Kingpins'%20Named%20In%20CBI's%201st%20NEET%20Chargesheet%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStating%20parents%20of%20some%20students%20had%20also%20been%20named%2C%20officials%20said%20the%20agency%20would%20file%20at%20least%20one%20supplementary%20chargesheet%20as%20investigations%20proceed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Justice%20also%20observed%20there%20is%20a%20need%20to%20have%20counselling%20programmes%20to%20ensure%20mental%20welfare%20of%20students%2C%20as%20well%20as%20training%20for%20staff%20and%20management%20to%20handle%20such%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BCan't%20Conclude%20Sanctity%20Breached%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%20the%20court%20ruled%20out%20a%20full%20re-test.%20Hearing%20a%20clutch%20of%20petitions%20asking%20for%20the%20exam%20to%20be%20held%20again%2C%20the%20court%20said%20it%20was%20not%20satisfied%20there%20was%20a%20large-scale%20breach%20of%20its%20%26quot%3Bsanctity%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthere-will-be-no-neet-re-exam-rules-supreme-court-6170722%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENo%20NEET%20Re-Exam%2C%20Court%20Says%20%26quot%3BCan't%20Conclude%20Sanctity%20Breached%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20admitted%20the%20paper%20had%20been%20leaked%20but%20said%20there%20was%20no%20material%20on%20record%20to%20conclude%20%26quot%3Bthe%20result%20of%20the%20exam%20was%20vitiated%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BData%20on%20record%20is%20not%20indicative%20of%20a%20systemic%20leak%20of%20the%20question%20paper%2C%20which%20would%20lead%20to%20the%20destruction%20of%20the%20sanctity%20of%20the%20exam...%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20court%20is%20(also)%20mindful%20of%20the%20fact%20directing%20a%20fresh%20exam%20would%20have%20serious%20consequences%20on%20students%2C%20including%20destruction%20of%20admission%20schedule%2C%20effects%20on%20education%2C%20and%20availability%20of%20medical%20professionals%20in%20the%20future.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20controversy%20over%20the%20exam%2C%20held%20May%205%2C%20broke%20after%20red%20flags%20were%20raised%20over%20the%20number%20-%2067%20-%20of%20perfect%20scores%2C%20including%20a%20coaching%20centre%20in%20Haryana's%20Bahadurgarh%20that%20produced%20six%20on%20its%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20also%20questions%20over%20the%20award%20of%20'grace%20marks'%20for%201%2C563%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20retest%20for%20those%201%2C563%20was%20held%2C%20but%20hundreds%20did%20not%20appear%20and%20many%20of%20those%20who%20did%20scored%20significantly%20fewer%20marks.%20This%20included%20the%20six%20from%20the%20Haryana%20centre%3B%20they%20got%20only%20682%20this%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20also%20a%20separate%20row%20over%20two%20'correct'%20answers%20for%20one%20question%20in%20the%20Physics%20section.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneet-ug-2024-paper-leak-question-that-supreme-court-asked-iit-to-solve-and-what-they-said-6168569%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20NEET%20Question%20Court%20Asked%20IIT%20To%20Solve%2C%20And%20What%20They%20Answered%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20referred%20the%20question%20to%20experts%20from%20IIT%20(Delhi).%20Subsequently%2C%20students%20who%20had%20picked%20what%20the%20experts%20said%20was%20the%20incorrect%20answer%20lost%20four%20marks.%C2%A0At%20least%2044%20students%2C%20who%20chose%20the%20alternative%20answer%2C%20received%20%26quot%3Bgrace%20marks%26quot%3B%20and%20achieved%20a%20perfect%20score%20of%20720%2F720.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%20is%20now%20available%20on%20WhatsApp%20channels.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatsapp.com%2Fchannel%2F0029Va4lixw7z4kcvZI9JM12%5C%22%3EClick%20on%20the%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20all%20the%20latest%20updates%20from%20NDTV%20on%20your%20chat.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722580200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fef9ofil8_supreme-court-generic_625x300_30_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-says-exam-body-nta-must-avoid-flip-flops-in-relation-to-neet-ug-exam-6245538%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20directed%20the%20National%20Testing%20Agency%20-%20the%20under-fire%20central%20body%20responsible%20for%20the%20conduct%20of%20the%20NEET-UG%20test%20-%20to%20%26quot%3Brectify%20deficiencies%20in%20the%20exam%20system%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonical