20winning%20a%20gold%20medal%20at%20the%20biggest%20of%20stages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhelif%20made%20her%20boxing%20debut%20as%20a%20professional%20in%202018%20World%20Championships%2C%20finishing%2017th.%20In%20the%202019%20edition%20of%20the%20event%2C%20she%20finished%2019th.%20Khelif%20then%20competed%20in%20the%20Tokyo%20Olympics%2C%20held%20in%202021%2C%20where%20she%20was%20knocked%20out%20by%20Ireland's%20Kellie%20Harrington%20in%20the%20quarter-finals.%20Khelif%20secured%20the%20second%20spot%20in%20the%20Women's%20World%20Boxing%20Championships%20after%20being%20defeated%20by%20Amy%20Broadhurst.%20She%20went%20on%20to%20win%20gold%20medals%20in%20the%202022%20African%20Championships%2C%20Mediterranean%20Games%20and%202023%20Arab%20Games%20the%20following%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC8NBkOBIAqO%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC8NBkOBIAqO%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC8NBkOBIAqO%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2F