ut%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIOC%20On%20Imane%20Khelif's%20Paris%20Olympics%20Qualification%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20International%20Olympic%20Committee%20spokesperson%20Mark%20Adams%20said%20that%20since%20Khelif's%20passport%20has%20'female'%20written%20on%20it%2C%20she%20is%20competing%20in%20the%20women's%20category%20in%20the%2066kg%20division.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEveryone%20competing%20in%20the%20women's%20category%20is%20complying%20with%20the%20competition%20eligibility%20rules%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20this%20week.%20%26quot%3BThey%20are%20women%20in%20their%20passports%2C%20and%20it's%20stated%20that%20this%20is%20the%20case%2C%20that%20they%20are%20female.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20current%20and%20former%20female%20boxing%20champions%20such%20as%20Claressa%20Shields%20and%20Ebanie%20Bridges%20have%20openly%20criticised%20the%20IOC%20for%20its%20ruling.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20COA%2C%20which%20is%20the%20Algerian%20Olympic%20Committee%2C%20has%20come%20out%20in%20support%20to%20Imane%20Khelif%20and%20lambasted%20the%20reports%20against%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722575340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fl9krh2q_imane-khelif-afp_625x300_02_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Folympics-2024%2Fwho-is-imane-khalif-the-algerian-boxer-at-center-of-gender-controversy-in-paris-olympics-6244664%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Algerian%20boxer%20Imane%20Khelif%20is%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20a%20major%20storm%20at%20the%20Paris%20Olympics%2C%20with%20the%20pugilist's%20participation%20in%20the%20women's%20category%20of%2066kg%20event%20being%20questioned.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A109%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Folympics-2024%2Fwho-is-imane-khalif-the-algerian-boxer-at-center-of-gender-controversy-in-paris-olympics-6244664%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.am