1%20million%20on%20its%20opening%20weekend%2C%20the%20sequel%20continues%20to%20explore%20the%20American%20West's%20expansion%20and%20settlement%20amidst%20the%20Civil%20War%20era.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fhollywood%2Fnews%2Fkevin-costners-horizon-an-american-saga-chapter-two-to-premiere-at-venice-film-festival%2Farticleshow%2F112212778.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Grow%20Your%20Microgreens%20Using%20This%20Portable%2C%20Chemical-Free%20Cultivator%20Made%20of%20Banana%20Pulp%20Waste%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EGrowing%20indoor%20plants%20in%20cities%20like%20Mumbai%20is%20a%20challenge%2C%20where%20space%20is%20a%20major%20constraint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESnehal%20Ambekar%20(22)%2C%20a%20Mumbai%20resident%2C%20faced%20these%20challenges%20when%20she%20tried%20growing%20microgreens%20at%20her%20house.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20usually%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20balconies%20to%20grow%20plants.%20They%20also%20need%20a%20lot%20of%20care%2C%20which%20becomes%20difficult%20in%20our%20hectic%20schedules.%20I%20failed%20in%20my%20experiments%20due%20to%20mould%20formation%20and%20wanted%20to%20find%20an%20easier%20way%20to%20grow%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20met%20Sayak%20Gupta%20(22)%20while%20pursuing%20a%20BTech%20in%20food%20technology%2C%20entrepreneurship%20and%20management%20from%20the%20National%20Institute%20of%20Food%20Technology%2C%20Entrepreneurship%20and%20Management%20%E2%80%93%20Kundli%20(NIFTEM-K)%20in%20Haryana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESnehal%E2%80%99s%20personal%20experience%2C%20combined%20with%20Sayak%E2%80%99s%20passion%20and%20their%20course%20knowledge%2C%20inspired%20them%20to%20develop%20an%20automated%20cultivator%20that%20helps%20%E2%80%9Cgrow%20your%20own%20vitamins%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20Snehal%20Ambekar%20and%20Sayak%20Gupta%2C%20two%20food%20technologists%2C%20devised%20a%20portable%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F349300%2Fhow-to-grow-microgreens-at-home-or-farm-aditi-mali-of-mali-greens-shares-tips%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esoilless%20microgreens%20cultivator%20%3C%2Fa%3Elabelled%20%E2%80%98Half%20Inch%20Garden%E2%80%99%20through%20their%20venture%20SS%20AgriQulture%20Innovations.%20What%20sets%20this%20cultivator%20apart%20is%20that%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20require%20any%20seeds.%20Instead%2C%20it%20comes%20with%20seed%20patches%20made%20from%20agricultural%20waste.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20friends%20are%20now%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20make%20growing%20superfoods%20convenient%20and%20accessible%20for%20everyone.%20Here%E2%80%99s%20how%20their%20journey%20started.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20garden%20that%20fits%20on%20your%20coffee%20table!%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Snehal%20Ambekar%20was%20just%2017%2C%20she%20faced%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F295026%2Fhealthcare-startup-to-manage-pcos-for-indian-women-by-sisters-raises-funding%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emultitude%20of%20health%20challenges%3C%2Fa%3E.%20She%20felt%20dizzy%20when%20she%20stood%20up%2C%20had%20blackouts%2C%20brain%20fog%2C%20sleep%20arthritis%2C%20and%20an%20overwhelming%20sense%20of%20fatigue.%20Things%20were%20so%20bad%20that%20this%20young%20girl%20was%20bedridden.%20She%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20focus%20on%20her%20studies%20or%20even%20step%20out%20of%20the%20house.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20during%20the%20advent%20of%20the%20pandemic%2C%20and%20since%20some%20of%20her%20symptoms%20matched%20with%20COVID-19%2C%20her%20parents%20had%20her%20tested%20for%20it.%20When%20she%20tested%20negative%2C%20the%20doctor%20suggested%20a%20complete%20blood%20checkup%20with%20tests%20%E2%80%94%20including%20thyroid%2C%20diabetes%2C%20iron%2C%20serum%20creatinine%2C%20Vitamin%20B12%2C%20D%2C%20B9%2C%20etc.%20This%20was%20followed%20by%20some%20X-rays%20and%20the%20result%20was%20clear%3A%20Snehal%20was%20nutritionally%20deficient.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20teenager%20was%20shocked.%20%E2%80%9CI%20ate%20home-cooked%20vegetarian%20meals%20and%20followed%20a%20healthy%20diet.%20I%20was%20young%2C%20healthy%2C%20and%20exercised%20regularly.%20How%20could%20I%20have%20a%20vitamin%20deficiency%3F%20I%20was%20in%20disbelief%2C%E2%80%9D%20Snehal%20recalls%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20diagnosis%20shed%20light%20on%20an%20often-overlooked%20aspect%20of%20nutrition%3A%20the%20potential%20for%20deficiency%20even%20in%20seemingly%20healthy%20diets.%20Moreover%2C%20her%20condition%20was%20compounded%20by%20a%20diagnosis%20of%20Polycystic%20Ovary%20Syndrome%20(PCOS)%2C%20a%20hormonal%20disorder.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20popping%20more%20than%2010%20pills%20a%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20Mumbai%20resident%2C%20who%20was%20then%20given%20a%20battery%20of%20medicines%20for%20different%20vitamin%20deficiencies%20and%20advised%20a%20complete%20overhaul%20in%20her%20diet%2C%20exercise%2C%20and%20overall%20lifestyle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20she%20buried%20herself%20in%20research%20to%20understand%20which%20foods%20were%20nutrient-dense%20and%20aid%20in%20a%20healthy%20life.%20One%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98superfoods%E2%80%99%20she%20found%20at%20this%20time%20was%20microgreens.%20Little%20did%20she%20realise%20then%20that%20she%20would%20be%20launching%20an%20associated%20startup%20with%20her%20classmate%2C%20Sayak%20Gupta%2C%20four%20years%20later!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-2-min-1722524050.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Snehal%20and%20Sayak%2C%20Founders%20of%20SS%20AgriQulture%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-2-min-1722524050.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-2-min-1722524050-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-2-min-1722524050-500x500.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-2-min-1722524050-150x150.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-2-min-1722524050-768x768.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FUntitled-design-2-min-1722524050-96x96.jpg%2096w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-359444%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESnehal%20and%20Sayak%2C%20Founders%20of%20SS%20AgriQulture%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESayak%20also%20had%20a%20deep%20passion%20for%20nutrition%20and%20wanted%20to%20develop%20a%20product%20that%20could%20make%20nutrition%20available%20to%20people%20in%20the%20comfort%20of%20their%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTraditionally%2C%20India%20has%20only%20focused%20on%20protein%2C%20while%20missing%20out%20on%20micronutrients.%20Vitamins%2C%20minerals%2C%20and%20phytonutrients%20are%20equally%20important%20and%20beneficial%20to%20us.%20We%20generally%20rely%20on%20supplements%20and%20medicines%20to%20get%20these%20nutrients.%20But%20nothing%20beats%20real%20food%2C%20which%20gives%20you%20good%20results%20in%20the%20long%20run%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sayak%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20example%2C%20beetroot%20microgreens%2C%20which%20are%20only%20one