%20a%20Pennsylvania%20rally%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20times%20purchases%20will%20defer%2C%20and%20people%20will%20come%20back%20and%20buy%20what%20they%20were%20going%20to%20buy%2C%20and%20other%20times%20that%20won't%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20sure%2C%20dealing%20with%20a%20wild%20news%20cycle%20isn't%20the%20only%20problem%20on%20Amazon's%20plate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20issuing%20a%20weak%20revenue%20forecast%2C%20the%20company%20also%20said%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-stock-amzn-quarterly-earnings-call-report-live-updates-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emissed%20sales%20estimates%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20second%20quarter%20of%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Olsavsky%2C%20the%20dip%20in%20sales%20was%20driven%20by%20a%20shift%20in%20consumer%20behavior%2C%20with%20people%20opting%20to%20be%20more%20frugal%20with%20their%20spending.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20seeing%20cautious%20consumers%2C%20they're%20looking%20for%20deals%2C%20they're%20trading%20down%20to%20lower%20ASP%20(average%20sales%20price)%20options%20when%20they%20can%2C%20and%20that%20hasn't%20changed%2C%26quot%3B%20Olsavsky%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20shift%20resulted%20in%20brisk%20sales%20for%20Amazon's%20lower-priced%20Everyday%20Essentials%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20far%20us%2C%20the%20volume%20of%20units%20sold%20actually%20accelerated%20slightly%20when%20you%20adjust%20for%20the%20leap%20year%20effect%20in%20Q1%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20just%20right%20now%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20traction%20is%20to%20lower%20ASP%20products%20and%20that%20is%20impacting%20the%20revenue%20growth%20a%20bit.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-cfo-blames-olympics-and-trump-assassination-for-slowing-sales-2024-8%5C%22%3EBusiness