r%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20was%20finally%20deemed%20worthy%20of%20a%20room%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-wealthy-investors-got-rich-looting-needy-hospitals-healthcare-system-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmerican%20hospital%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20was%20shown%20to%20a%20bed.%20I%20did%20not%20want%20to%20be%20on%20a%20bed.%20I%20knew%20from%20birthing%20my%20first%20child%20that%20lying%20on%20a%20bed%20was%20the%20most%20uncomfortable%20position%20of%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20knew%20because%20the%20Swiss%20and%20German%20midwives%20who%20had%20attended%20the%20birth%20of%20my%20first%20child%20had%20prompted%20me%20to%20try%20almost%20every%20position%20and%20option%20they%20knew%20of%20to%20find%20what%20would%20make%20me%20the%20most%20comfortable.%20Yet%20when%20I%20continued%20to%20request%20an%20alternative%20situation%20at%20the%20US%20hospital%2C%20the%20nurse%20gave%20me%20an%20oxygen%20mask%20instead%2C%20perhaps%20to%20keep%20me%20quiet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d561c2ff-0340-4dcb-a498-f80d52f28cba%5C%22%3EI%20felt%20lucky%20not%20to%20be%20a%20first-time%20mom%20in%20America%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20major%20difference%20was%20the%20overall%20level%20of%20care%2C%20both%20in%20the%20hospital%20and%20outside%20it.%20In%20Switzerland%2C%20the%20standard%20of%20care%20is%20a%20five-day%20hospital%20stay%20for%20a%20vaginal%20birth%20and%20a%2010-day%20hospital%20stay%20for%20a%20C-section.%20Despite%20having%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pbs.org%2Fnewshour%2Fshow%2Fhow-switzerland-delivered-health-care-for-all-and-kept-its-private-insurance%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprivate%20insurer-based%3C%2Fa%3E%20system%20like%20the%20US%2C%20the%20Swiss%20system%20is%20tightly%20regulated%20by%20a%20government%20that%20acknowledges%20that%20there's%20a%20basic%20level%20of%20care%20that%20all%20people%20deserve.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20includes%20the%20belief%