EPeterson-KFF%20Health%20System%20Tracker%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It's%20a%20staggering%20price%20to%20pay%20by%20world%20standards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224a1cc28a-748b-4aa8-abbb-2f483bbccfe6%5C%22%3EThe%20system%20in%20the%20US%20felt%20broken%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFive%20years%20later%2C%20I%20haven't%20been%20able%20to%20shed%20the%20feeling%20that%20something%20is%20wrong%20with%20the%20care%20in%20my%20own%20country.%20That%20we%20all%20deserve%20better.%20Especially%20considering%20we%20are%20paying%20so%20much%20more%20for%20so%20much%20less.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20experience%20is%20only%20mine%2C%20but%20statistics%20also%20show%20that%20there%20are%20problems%20behind%20the%20state%20of%20care%20in%20America.%20In%20June%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.commonwealthfund.org%2Fpublications%2Fissue-briefs%2F2024%2Fjun%2Finsights-us-maternal-mortality-crisis-international-comparison%23%3A~%3Atext%3DRecent%2520Maternal%2520Mortality%2520Trends%2Cdeaths%2520per%2520100%252C000%2520live%2520births.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECommonwealth%20Fund%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20that%20more%20women%20in%20the%20US%20are%20dying%20of%20pregnancy-related%20complications%20than%20in%20any%20other%20developed%20country.%20In%202022%2C%20the%20rate%20for%20infant%20mortality%20in%20the%20US%20also%20increased%2C%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Fnchs%2Fdata%2Fvsrr%2Fvsrr033.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECenters%20for%20Disease%20Control%20and%20Prevention%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20left%20feeling%20that%20healthcare%20doesn't%20have%20to%20be%20like%20this%20%E2%80%94%20I%20know%20from%20experience%20that%20in%20other%20wealthy%20countries%2C%20it%20isn't.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EChantal%20Panozzo%20is%20writing%20a%20book%20about%20what%20she%20wishes%20she'd%20known%20about%20American%20life%20before%20giving%20up%20her%20Swiss%20residency%20permit.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EGot%20a%20personal%20essay%