20at%20the%20peak%20of%20the%20AI-driven%20supercycle%20just%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20rising%20demand%20for%20electricity%20due%20to%20digitalization%2C%20AI%2C%20and%20the%20use%20of%20renewable%20energies%20are%20increasing%20the%20demand%20for%20metal%20raw%20materials%2C%26quot%3B%20Thomas%20Rupf%2C%20chief%20investment%20officer%20at%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eprivate%20bank%20VP%20Bank%20in%20Asia%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20still%20too%20early%20to%20declare%20a%20new%20super%20cycle%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20there%20are%20still%20investment%20opportunities%20in%20areas%20like%20industrial%20metals%20and%20mining%2C%20both%20boosted%20by%20AI%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ey.com%2Fen_sg%2Fpeople%2Fjosie-ananto%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJosie%20Ananto%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20principal%20at%20EY-Parthenon's%20strategy%20and%20transactions%20team%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20growing%20ubiquity%20of%20chips%20means%20that%20demand%20will%20be%20a%20lot%20more%20persistent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20growth%20of%20the%20semiconductor%20sector%20is%20not%20a%20hype%20%E2%80%94%20it%20is%20real%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BFor%20example%2C%20electric%20vehicles%20in%20the%20automotive%20sector%2C%20product%20innovation%20in%20life%20sciences%20and%20pharmaceutical%20sector%2C%20consumer%20recommendation%20and%20personalization%20in%20the%20consumer%20products%20and%20retail%20sector.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22db60ded9-1262-458a-9178-d6d9653eccbb%5C%22%3EHeightened%20competition%20will%20only%20make%20things%20harder%20for%20incumbents%20like%20Nvidia%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESemiconductor%20supercycle%20aside%2C%20investors%20may%20also%20want%20to%20pay%20attention%20to%20the%20competitive%20dynamics%20for%20chip%20designers%20like%20Nvidia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNvidia%20today%20is%20the%20leader%20in%20producing%20chips%20for%20AI%20training%20and%20deployment%2C%26quot%3B%20Miller%20said.%20%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20Nvidia's%20success%20is%20already%20attracting%20competition.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20TSMC%2C%20Nvidia%20designs%20but%20doesn't%20make%20its%20own%20chips.%20This%2C%20Miller%20added%2C%20means%20that%20Nvidia%20is%20exposed%20to%20multiple%20threats%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20it%20be%20from%20Big%20Tech%20players%20like%20Meta%20and%20Google%20or%20startups%20like%20Groq.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20barrier%20to%20entry%20for%20chip%20manufacturing%20is%20very%20high%2C%20given%20the%20significant%20capital%20investment%20required%20to%20open%20a%20fabrication%20plant%2C%26quot%3B%20EY-Parthenon's%20Ananto%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20chip%20design%2C%20however%2C%20this%20is%20an%20area%20that%20is%20likely%20ripe%20for%20disruption%2C%20as%20more%20technology%20companies%20are%20investing%20in%20chip%20design%20capabilities%2C%20specifically%20tailored%20to%20their%20products%20with%20faster%20time%20to%20market%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-nvidia-aws-ai-chip-dominance-gpu-trainium-inferentia-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmazon%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fabout.fb.com%2Fnews%2F2024%2F04%2Fintroducing-our-next-generation-infrastructure-for-ai%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMeta%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcloud.google.com%2Fblog%2Fproducts%2Fcompute%2Fintroducing-googles-new-arm-based-cpu%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20all%20designing%20their%20own%20AI%20chips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20Nvidia%20isn't%20standing%20still%2C%20either.%20In%20May%2C%20Nvidia%20CEO%20Jensen%20Huang%20said%20the%20company%20would%20release%20new%20chips%20on%20a%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-demand-ai-chips-blackwell-hopper-ceo-jensen-huang-earnings