y%20decided%20to%20land%2C%20they%20did%20not%20choose%20the%20closest%20airfield.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20immediately%20clear%20from%20the%20report%20that%20the%20crew%20had%20any%20other%20indications%20that%20something%20was%20seriously%20wrong%20with%20their%20aircraft%2C%20and%20Conley%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bthis%20is%20the%20first%20time%20that%20this%20specific%20part%20has%20failed%20on%20a%20V-22%20of%20any%20any%20type%20in%20almost%20800%2C000%20flight%20hours.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20three-star%20general%20and%20V-22%20pilot%20also%20described%20the%20warnings%20the%20crew%20was%20seeing%20as%20%26quot%3Bkind%20of%20like%20a%20check%20engine%20light%20in%20your%20car%20%E2%80%94%20you%20could%20drive%20your%20car%20for%2010%20years%20and%20not%20get%20any%20or%20you%20could%20drive%20next%20week%20and%20get%20three%20different%20ones%20for%20multiple%20reasons.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConley%20told%20reporters%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20chips%20are%20a%20byproduct%20of%20just%20the%20gearboxes%20themselves.%20%E2%80%A6%20It's%20not%20unique%20to%20a%20V-22%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20the%20first%20five%20alarms%20meant%20%26quot%3Bthat%20the%20detector%20had%20detected%20the%20chip%20and%20successfully%20burned%20it%20off.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20confirmed%20that%20the%20pilots%20%26quot%3Bfollowed%20their%20training%20to%20read%20the%20checklists%20and%20to%20look%20for%20secondary%20indications%2C%26quot%3B%20undercutting%20the%20report's%20conclusion%20that%20the%20pilots%20took%20unnecessary%20risks%20with%20%26quot%3Ba%20potentially%20serious%20mechanical%20problem.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20he%20said%20the%20crew's%20actions%20contributed%20to%20the%20mishap%2C%20Conley%20told%20reporters%20that%20%26quot%3Bthere's%20nothing%20to%20indicate%20that%20they%20did%20anything%20deliberately%20to%20violate%20any%20policy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20crash%2C%20AFSOC%20protocol%20has%20changed%2C%20and%20c