e%20that%20you%20are%20meant%20to%20be%20different%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added%20in%20the%20same%20talk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20age%20of%2013%2C%20he%20had%20learned%20the%20ropes%20of%20cooking%20and%20started%20helping%20his%20mother%20sell%20%3Cem%3Echole%20bhature%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20schools.%20He%20was%20the%20sous%20chef%20in%20his%20mother%E2%80%99s%20business%2C%20%E2%80%98Lawrence%20Garden%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20banquet%20hall.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETragedy%20struck%20a%20decade%20later%2C%20when%20the%20banquets%20were%20crushed%20by%20local%20authorities%2C%20shattering%20their%20dreams.%20Heartbroken%2C%20Vikas%20moved%20to%20New%20York%20to%20start%20a%20new%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201024px)%20100vw%2C%201024px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fchef-vikas-khanna-1722511088.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chef%20Vikas%20Khanna%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fchef-vikas-khanna-1722511088.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fchef-vikas-khanna-1722511088-300x200.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fchef-vikas-khanna-1722511088-500x333.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fchef-vikas-khanna-1722511088-768x512.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fchef-vikas-khanna-1722511088-150x100.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-359328%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22682%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EChef%20Vikas%20Khanna%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20New%20York%2C%20he%20took%20on%20nearly%2031%20odd%20jobs%2C%20including%20washing%20dishes%2C%20cleaning%20and%20cooking%20in%20homes%2C%20working%20in%20delis%2C%20cafes%2C%20and%20restaurants.%20He%20even%20looked%20after%20dogs%20and%20cats.%20He%20also%20worked%20in%20several%20restaurants%2C%20opened%20a%20cooking%20school%2C%20and%20ran%20catering%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20working%20in%20a%20restaurant%20in%20Paris%2C%20the%20chef%20told%20him%2C%20%E2%80%9CBlack%20hands%20don%E2%80%99t%20cook%2C%20they%20only%20clean.%E2%80%9D%20Khanna%20quit%20the%20next%20minute%20and%20vowed%20to%20show%20the%20chef%20what%20black%20hands%20can%20do!%20%E2%80%9CI%20will%20achieve%20something%20one%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20promised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202010%2C%20he%20returned%20to%20New%20York%20and%20opened%20a%20restaurant%20called%20Junoon%2C%20earning%20a%20Michelin%20Star%20the%20next%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20Vikas%20has%20not%20looked%20back%2C%20taking%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F335353%2Fharish-closepet-masterchef-india-father-cooking-school-lunchbox%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndian%20food%20and%20culture%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20world.%20In%202024%2C%20he%20opened%20a%20restaurant%20%E2%80%98Bungalow%E2%80%99%20in%20New%20York%2C%20which%20he%20calls%20his%20%E2%80%98last%20innings%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20hospitality%20industry.%20Bungalow%E2%80%99s%20reservations%20were%20sold%20out%20in%20just%2011%20seconds!%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20can%20take%20everything%20from%20you%2C%20but%20not%20your%20pride%20and%20happiness%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Khushi%20Arora%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722514832000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fchef-vikas-khanna-1722511088.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D359321%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chef%20Vikas%20Khanna's%20hard%20work%20conquered%20all%20the%20challenges%20on%20his%20way.%20Star